Description: A simplistic, modern markdown reader and editor
 MDFlex is a clean, modern application for reading and
 editing markdown documents. It features:
 .
  * Live preview of markdown content
  * Dark and light theme support
  * Read and write mode toggle
  * Full markdown syntax support
  * Export to HTML
  * Word and character count
 .
 Built with Python and PyQt6 for a native desktop experience.
